data.description: Want out of town, yet still close to everything? This 4 bedroom, 2 bath double wide is ready for you! Approximately 15 minutes from Ruby Hospital and 4.1 miles to University Town Center.  This large lot gives you a plenty of space. It also has a section up behind the house that has utilities to it for a second home or workshop.
